data.description: Looking for a big modern home with the charm of a classic Iowa farmhouse? I found it! Come take a look at this 4 bed, 4 bath updated home filled with modern conveniences and room to spread out! A Master Suite on the main floor and 3 generous bedrooms with their own upstairs bath make this home ideal for everyone on the list! Enjoy the patio out back and almost half an acre of well landscaped and private green space! Heated bathroom floor, walkout basement, second 1+ car garage in the basement, 2 year old Riding Lawn Mower and Snowblower included, all appliances were new in 2021 and are included. Too much to list, call or email for a private showing today and see it in person! reach out to Ian with Bickford Realty, 515-446-9094 or iansellsfd@gmail.com
